displayName: Jinami, the City of Martial Arts - Mercenary Corps' Rental House

parameters:
Novice Swordsman Auto: Eeek!? Ah, ah, it's Clea-san and the
others...
Mage Relm: This is more serious than I thought...

Novice Swordsman Auto: I've lost in battles many times and
there have been moments where I was almost killed.

Novice Swordsman Auto: I heard rumors that there are
participants who take pleasure in killing people in the
arena.
Clea: So, you can't stop trembling?

Novice Swordsman Auto: I've already decided to participate
in tomorrow's match. But if my opponent is a pleasure
killer... just thinking about it...
Clea: I understand. Please take a sword right away.

Thief Nora: D-Doing something like that would have the
opposite effect, you know!

Clea: If you said you want to become a splendid mercenary
like your father, then risking your life should be something
you do on a daily basis.
Clea: Or are you giving up on becoming a mercenary?

Novice Swordsman Auto: I-I can't do that. I want to become
a man like my father or Gale-san.

Clea: Then let's fight. I'll remind you of the path your
heart should be heading towards.
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Will you have a duel with the apprentice swordsman, Auto?

Apprentice swordsman Auto: I would be happy if I didn't
have to fight...

Clea: Please come at me seriously, Auto-san, without
holding back.

Apprentice swordsman Auto: This is completely different
from before... The pressure is incredible...!
クレアの決闘戦闘あり
Mage Relm: Hey, what do you want!?

Priestess Sophia: Hehe, I'm sure Clea-chan has something in
mind.

Apprentice swordsman Auto: I really can't do anything... I
can never become like my father, who was so confident...

Clea: I want to use rough treatment. Please leave me alone
with Auto-san until tomorrow morning.
Thief Nora: I-Is this going to be even rougher treatment!?

Clea: Please don't worry. I want you to understand my
determination as an adventurer.

Apprentice swordsman Auto: Yes, my strong point is
durability.
Clea: Is that so? Then please move to the bed.

Apprentice swordsman Auto: I understand, I will follow
your instructions, even if it means resting like that...
Would you like to skip the adult scene?
3.イベント後のプレイヤーの位置
Clea: I will keep going until I win, I will never give up.

Apprentice swordsman Auto: To think I would have to fight
again...
